[12:30 pm, 12/3/2026] Aaftab Charoliya: IPL 2025 Data Analysis Dashboard

Project Overview

This project analyzes IPL 2025 cricket data using Power BI. The goal of this project is to understand player performance, match statistics, and venue analysis through interactive dashboards.

Tools Used

- Power BI
- Excel / CSV Dataset

Dashboard Insights

- Total Runs scored in IPL 2025
- Total Wickets taken
- Top Batsmen based on runs
- Top Bowlers based on wickets
- Matches played by city

Features

- Interactive dashboard
- City filter for match analysis
- Player performance visualization
- Professional Power BI design

File

- IPL_PRO.pbix (Power BI dashboard file)

Author

Data Analytics Project
